('-6CgEzqeZFk', 'So What IF loads of fireworks exploded in my Van', 'To get COLINFURZE MERCH click here\nhttps://www.colinfurzeshop.com\n\nAfter collecting the huge amount of fireworks needed for the Deathstar project people asked if transporting was dangerous and what if they went of in the van, well this seemed like a question worth answering and as my old van was going scrap yard it seemed fitting to give it one last job.\nThanks to https://epicfireworks.com for supplying.\n\nCheck out my other firework videos here\n\n300 Rockets https://youtu.be/yQf5cGPcP48\nGiant Wheel https://youtu.be/tY5Wzjk0-Xs\nDeathstar https://youtu.be/gEUBLIFMgnY\n\nFollow me on social media here\nTwitter https://twitter.com/colin_furze\nInstagram https://www.instagram.com/realcolinfurze/\nFacebook https://www.facebook.com/Colin-furze-521680751253584\n\nSubscribe cis it\'s a dam good channel', '2016-10-13', 1, NULL),
