('0d5ntPLnn78', 'Squeezing a 600cc engine in to a Tuk Tuk (Far Cry 4)', 'So to celebrate the release of Far Cry 4 i thought i\'d take something in the game and make it a reality which is driving a Tuk Tuk and shooting stuff but it seemed a waste to leave the wimpy 150cc moped engine in it so here we have a nice CBR600 100bhp lump to wedge in.\n\nNext video we tackel the weapons\n\nFar Cry 4 is available on PlayStation 3 and PlayStation 4 on 18.11.14\n\nVisit the official Far Cry 4 website: http://bit.ly/1vDDoSG\n\nThis video was made with the support of Ubisoft.\n\nMore info and pictures on my website here http://www.colinfurze.com/tuk-tuk.html\n\nSUBSCRIBE IF YOU LOVE THIS STUFF\n\nTo get COLINFURZE MERCH click here\nhttps://www.colinfurzeshop.com\n\nfollow me on twitter https://twitter.com/colin_furze\n\nand my Facebook page https://www.facebook.com/pages/Colin-furze/521680751253584\n\n2nd song is by band called red house glory but its a vocaless track however here is there soundcloud\n\nhttps://soundcloud.com/redhouseglory', '2014-11-06', 1, '2nd song is by band called red house glory but its a vocaless track however here is there soundcloud\r\n\r\nhttps://soundcloud.com/redhouseglory'),
