('2esw8U2NENo', '1000 ROCKET BIKE', 'To get a COLINFURZE MERCH click here\nhttps://www.colinfurzeshop.com\n\n1000 Rockets all set of at once of the back of a custom bike while i\'m riding it.......but its ok i have some foam strapped to my back and my safety tie on.\nThanks to all that have subscribed watched and shared my videos.\n\nPre Order my book here http://smarturl.it/C-Furze\n\nSee my other Firework milestones here\n\nCheck out the other milestone Firework madness here\n1M - https://youtu.be/yQf5cGPcP48\n2M - https://youtu.be/tY5Wzjk0-Xs\n3M - https://youtu.be/gEUBLIFMgnY\n4M - https://youtu.be/5-e2tAUo89o\n5M - https://youtu.be/2esw8U2NENo\n6M - 6M - https://youtu.be/fzMi6yf1Roc\n7M - https://youtu.be/Jtols_QhuWw\n\nBig thanks to Epic as they supply the Fireworks, Go visit them\nhttps://epicfireworks.com\n\nBehind the scenes from the drone guy karl https://youtu.be/qZsloahpiUQ\n\nSocial stuff here people\nTwitter https://twitter.com/colin_furze\nInstagram https://www.instagram.com/realcolinfurze/\nFacebook https://www.facebook.com/Colin-furze-521680751253584\n\nMUSIC\n\n1st track is by \"Revenge of the Psychotronic Man\" and is called \"The Establishment\" you can find more on them here.\nhttps://revengeofthepsychotronicman.bandcamp.com\n\n2nd Track is called \"Always Forward\" and is by \"Alive Again\"you can find more on them here.\nhttp://aliveagain.bandcamp.com\n\nIn a band, want your music on my videos! Send your tracks to furzemail@yahoo.co.uk as all music on this channel is from viewer\'s\n\n#fireworks #furze #amazing', '2017-08-24', 1, '1st track is by \"Revenge of the Psychotronic Man\" and is called \"The Establishment\" you can find more on them here.\r\nhttps://revengeofthepsychotronicman.bandcamp.com\r\n\r\n2nd Track is called \"Always Forward\" and is by \"Alive Again\"you can find more on them here.\r\nhttp://aliveagain.bandcamp.com'),
