('8UKNajCgpEs', 'Apocalyptic BUNKER project part 1- The Plan', 'An UNDERGROUND BUNKER in the back garden, i have dreamt of this for a while now to go with my superhero mods and crazy inventions so when asked what i would do if faced with the end of the world the 2 ideas become one and so here we go i\'m building a full scale full on bunker in my own back yard........and someone else is paying muhahahaha.\n\nBe sure to subscribe and check out the rest of the process of building the underground bunker.\n\nTo get COLINFURZE MERCH click here\nhttps://www.colinfurzeshop.com\n\nThis video is paid-for advertorial. #ad\n\nMore from Sky1 - http://www.sky.com/tv/channel/sky1\nWatch more from Sky1 - https://www.youtube.com/user/skyonezone\nFind out more about the You, Me & The Apocalypse here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nnFTbj7QyBE\nFollow Sky on Twitter @Sky1 #ApocalypseSky1\n\nMusic is by \"Heroic\" and the song is called \"charity for nothing\"\n\nWebsite: www.heroicofficial.com\nSpotify: https://play.spotify.com/album/164oRDAAP6ZTz9sU05tSYA', '2015-09-15', 1, 'Music is by \"Heroic\" and the song is called \"charity for nothing\"\r\n\r\nWebsite: www.heroicofficial.com\r\nSpotify: https://play.spotify.com/album/164oRDAAP6ZTz9sU05tSYA'),
