('BiYkAlTT1MU', 'Behind the Scenes, what goes into to making a video and blowing up drones in the bunker.', 'To get COLINFURZE MERCH click here\nhttps://www.colinfurzeshop.com\n\nMaking a video is a lot of work (hence why i only put out one a week) but some videos need a bit extra so they stand apart from whats gone before them.\nSo for the Deus Ex project i turned the bunker in to a dark industrial scene simlar to whats found in the game, also as i needed to blow things up and shoot fireworks from my arm, a steel box under the ground is not a bad place to start.\nWith all this in mind we set to work......its all fun n games lol\n\nCheck out the finished video here https://youtu.be/aR4TsEjpQyM\n\nAnd the other crazy film and game inspired builds here\nhttps://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLGjbAdaOBLBnRDNW4Awc7nnT0wovCCt9l\n\nThe Project itself was supported by Square Enix but this video is pure furze\n\nFollow me on social media shite here\n\nTWITTER https://twitter.com/colin_furze\nFACEBOOK https://www.facebook.com/Colin-furze-...\n\nMusic\n\nSong 1 \"Ginchy\" by \"Balu & die Surfgrammeln\" http://bit.ly/2bPomrL\nSong 2 \"Clash Culture \" by \"March to the Grave\" http://apple.co/2bPmorx', '2016-09-01', 1, 'Song 1 \"Ginchy\" by \"Balu & die Surfgrammeln\" http://bit.ly/2bPomrL\r\nSong 2 \"Clash Culture \" by \"March to the Grave\" http://apple.co/2bPmorx'),
('CJlKYk9lbqg', 'How should I modify this guitar', 'To get COLINFURZE MERCH click here\nhttps://www.colinfurzeshop.com\n\nThere\'s a new show starting called \"Americas Greatest Makers\" and although I hope I get you excited about making things on a weekly basis I\'ve teamed up with the show\'s sponsors Intel to get behind why making stuff is so great.\nSo I\'d like your ideas on what mods to make to a guitar to mask my terrible guitar skills and make me feel like a rock god as making things is not just about making your life easier or to speed up a task....\n\nFind out more about the show here http://bit.ly/PH1YT\n\nUse the hashtag #AmericasGreatestMakers when doing all that social media jazz you people like so much\n\nSubscribe so not to miss what i make.', '2016-04-05', 1, NULL),
('CxLWwFnZrL8', 'Larking around at Silverstone', 'This video came about after asking a question i was expecting the to be NO for. I\'d been invited to silverstone by pole position youtube channel to attend some conference about silverstone and what not and i nearly didn\'t go. While i was there i asked if i could have ago in there 2 seater hyper sonic car and not only did they agree to that i convinced them to let me take the van round and the not quiet finished mobility scooter i had in the back (i\'d just taken it for the brake-line to be made up so the brakes did\'t work which is why i,m using my feet to stop at the grid on the drag race, but i didn\'t mention this on the day) so all in all a bloody good set of people. So excuse the filming as we only had a few laps with each machine so its a bit patchy but you get the vibe.\n\nCheck my other pages for news and pictures\nTwitter https://twitter.com/colin_furze\nInstagram https://www.instagram.com/realcolinfurze/\nFacebook https://www.facebook.com/Colin-furze-521680751253584\nhttp://www.colinfurze.com\n\nAnd thanks to Silverstone you can book you ride in the hypersonic car here and at £69 its pretty good value, plus its the closest most of us will get to experiencing a single seater race car.\n\nhttp://www.silverstone.co.uk/experiences/driving-days/the-hypersonic-ultimate-thrill1/\n\nThe music is by a swedish band called HEROIC you can see them here\n\nWebsite: www.heroicofficial.com\nSpotify: https://play.spotify.com/album/164oRDAAP6ZTz9sU05tSYA\n\nENJOY AND TELL PEOPLE THEY WILL SMILE', '2014-04-03', 1, 'The music is by a swedish band called HEROIC you can see them here\r\n\r\nWebsite: www.heroicofficial.com\r\nSpotify: https://play.spotify.com/album/164oRDAAP6ZTz9sU05tSYA'),
