('OqLi6lrOCzs', 'DIY X-MEN Making MAGNETO shoes', 'The whole process of making the magnets and testing there strenght.but will i be able to walk upside down?\nWhat i love about this is had i not been so tight i would have bought some stronger factory made magnets and missed all the fun of stripping down the mircowaves , so what i\'m saying is its good to be tight with your money.\n\nTheres more DIY X-MEN to come next thursday so subscribe you won\'t want to miss it.\n\nYou can see me learn to walk upside down here\n\nhttp://youtu.be/wr-7zcUuS90\n\nAnd see them in there full glory here\n\nhttp://youtu.be/uRKHCRR9-C4\n\nCheck my other pages for news and pictures\nTwitter https://twitter.com/colin_furze\nInstagram https://www.instagram.com/realcolinfurze/\nFacebook https://www.facebook.com/Colin-furze-521680751253584\nhttp://www.colinfurze.com\n\nMusic is by march to the grave and can be found here. First song is \"stamford stomp\" and the second song is \"whose chicken\"\n\nhttps://itunes.apple.com/us/artist/march-to-the-grave/id293740174?uo=4\n\nENJOY AND REMEMBER LIKE SAID THIS THE BEST CHANNEL AND I\'M NOT JUST SAYING THAT.', '2014-05-22', 1, 'Music is by march to the grave and can be found here. First song is \"stamford stomp\" and the second song is \"whose chicken\"'),
