('VmvcirebyY4', 'Making the hidden blade from Assassins Creed', 'The Assassin\'s creed hidden blade is the most iconic game gadget i know so we had to make it.\n\nThis video was made with the support of Ubisoft but myself and ubisoft must stress this was made for theatrical and promotional purposes only and should not be recreated, Parts of this build video have been purposely missed or details not shown, the item is decommissioned every time filming is finished.\n\nSubscribe for videos like this\n\nSee the first ep here https://youtu.be/4OyoWAZEcIE\n\nsee the 2nd ep here https://youtu.be/arbNxONg88c\n\nsee them in action here https://youtu.be/ESFewdU0JcA\n\nAssassin’s Creed Syndicate is out on PlayStation 4 and Xbox One on 23.10.15 and PC 19.11.15\nTry out the XIXTH Century Search Engine for Assassin’s Creed Syndicate here: http://ubi.li/qc5hd\n\nThe music is by \"Freeze the Atlantic\" and the first track is \"Occams Razor\" and the second \"Welcome back to Nibelhiem\"\nmore info here\nWeb Site: www.freezetheatlantic.co.uk\n\nYouTube: https://www.youtube.com/user/FreezeTheAtlanticUK\n\nFacebook Page: www.facebook.com/freezetheatlantic\n\nLabel: www.ilovealcopop.co.uk\n\n\nTo get COLINFURZE MERCH click here\nhttps://www.colinfurzeshop.com', '2015-11-24', 1, 'The music is by \"Freeze the Atlantic\" and the first track is \"Occams Razor\" and the second \"Welcome back to Nibelhiem\"\r\nmore info here\r\nWeb Site: www.freezetheatlantic.co.uk\r\n\r\nYouTube: https://www.youtube.com/user/FreezeTheAtlanticUK\r\n\r\nFacebook Page: www.facebook.com/freezetheatlantic\r\n\r\nLabel: www.ilovealcopop.co.uk'),
('VsRot0p7ObY', 'The Washing Machine that would not Die', 'To get a COLINFURZE MERCH click here\nhttps://www.colinfurzeshop.com\n\nSo fireworks night is coming and haven\'t destroyed anything for a laugh in ages so as i\'m working on a massive project in a barn i thought i\'d take the opportunity to go outside and send some rockets in a washing machine but the fun was mostly found in fixing it only to take more abuse........Rock On Washing Machine.\n\nTo see more Fire work madness check out this playlist\nhttps://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLGjbAdaOBLBl8Nj49ru3KDeNN9FEQ02wE\n\nTo see the Firework launcher being made click here\nhttps://youtu.be/IBus-OpyX5c\n\nSocial stuff here people\nTwitter https://twitter.com/colin_furze\nInstagram https://www.instagram.com/realcolinfurze/\nFacebook https://www.facebook.com/Colin-furze-521680751253584\n\nMusic\n\nBoth Tracks are by \"Diamond in the Dirt\" and the tracks \"hopeless\" and \"Burning Hair\" more on them here https://diamondinthedirt.bandcamp.com\n\nIn a band, want your music on my videos! Send your tracks to furzemail@yahoo.co.uk as all music on this channel is from viewer\'s', '2017-11-02', 1, 'Both Tracks are by \"Diamond in the Dirt\" and the tracks \"hopeless\" and \"Burning Hair\" more on them here https://diamondinthedirt.bandcamp.com'),
('Wear7sR65-o', 'WALL OF DEATH Teaching a man that sold his life Part 2 of 2', 'Check my other pages for news and pictures\nTwitter https://twitter.com/colin_furze\nInstagram https://www.instagram.com/realcolinfurze/\nFacebook https://www.facebook.com/Colin-furze-521680751253584\nhttp://www.colinfurze.com\n\nIan Usher sold his whole life on ebay (everything job house the lot) then set himself a list of 100 goals to complete in 100 weeks one of his goals was to ride a wall of death. Ian did really well to ride the wall even though some people will proberly say \"he didn\'t get very high\" since i built this thing the weather has taken its toll and even i struggle to ride it like i used to.\n\nTo find out more about Ians story you can visit his websites\n\n100goals100weeks.com\n\nianusher.com\n\nHe has just wrote a book about his whole story which is avalible on amazon and is called.  A LIFE SOLD.\n\nwww.ianusher.com/ALifeSold.php\n\nMUSIC by March to the Grave\n\nFor more info on anything you can email me at\n\ncolinfurze@yahoo.co.uk', '2011-01-21', 1, 'MUSIC by March to the Grave'),
('WiWAcuMZ-ls', 'Homemade Machine Gun Briefcase from The Kingsman', 'Never mind Eggsy its Furzey. Fine job I made of this I say.\n\nSee other film and Video game gadgets in this amazing playlist, hidden blades, wolverine claws grapple hooks n shields.\n\nhttps://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLGjbAdaOBLBnRDNW4Awc7nnT0wovCCt9l\n\nFollow me on Social Media\nInstagram https://www.instagram.com/realcolinfurze/\nTwitter https://twitter.com/colin_furze\nFacebook https://www.facebook.com/Colin-furze-521680751253584\n\nMusic\n\n1st Track is by \"KeyFrame\" and the track mis called \"Odd Socks\"\nhttps://www.facebook.com/pg/keyframesheffield/videos/?ref=page_internal\n\n2nd Track is by \"Braincoats\" and is called  \"I Need a Doctor\"\nhttps://www.facebook.com/BRAINCOATS/\nhttps://braincoats.bandcamp.com/\n\n3rd and 4th track is called \"Wrong\" and \"I\'m Shaking\"  is by \"Nosebleed\"\nBandcamp: https://nosebleedband.bandcamp.com\nFacebook: www.facebook.com/nosebleedband\nInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/nosebleedleeds/\nSpotify: https://open.spotify.com/artist/4gEoL67ta59CysHdWWK3Ld\n\nIn a band? Want your music on my videos! Send your tracks to furzemail@yahoo.co.uk as all music on this channel is from viewers\n\n#colinfurze #kingsman #briefcasegun', '2019-05-02', 1, '1st Track is by \"KeyFrame\" and the track mis called \"Odd Socks\"\r\nhttps://www.facebook.com/pg/keyframesheffield/videos/?ref=page_internal\r\n\r\n2nd Track is by \"Braincoats\" and is called  \"I Need a Doctor\"\r\nhttps://www.facebook.com/BRAINCOATS/\r\nhttps://braincoats.bandcamp.com/\r\n\r\n3rd and 4th track is called \"Wrong\" and \"I\'m Shaking\"  is by \"Nosebleed\"\r\nBandcamp: https://nosebleedband.bandcamp.com\r\nFacebook: www.facebook.com/nosebleedband\r\nInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/nosebleedleeds/\r\nSpotify: https://open.spotify.com/artist/4gEoL67ta59CysHdWWK3Ld'),
('Ws1W7jOe53w', '#Made for you Play Button', 'To get a COLINFURZE MERCH click here\nhttps://www.colinfurzeshop.com\n\nThe #madeforyou youtube campaign is about celebrating the unique connection between a channel and its viewers so they gave me this play button and asked me to make a video so i thought i\'d tweak the button to something more furze like and say thanks for all you as viewers do to the channel.\nNext week it\'s been 10 years so stay tuned for some special videos\n\nAND SUBSCRIBE https://www.youtube.com/user/colinfurze?sub_confirmation=1\n\nSocial stuff here people\nTwitter https://twitter.com/colin_furze\nInstagram https://www.instagram.com/realcolinfurze/\nFacebook https://www.facebook.com/Colin-furze-521680751253584\n\nMusic is by \"Revenge of the psychotronic man\" and the track is \"Rrose Selavy\" find more on them here\nhttps://revengeofthepsychotronicman.bandcamp.com', '2016-11-13', 1, 'Music is by \"Revenge of the psychotronic man\" and the track is \"Rrose Selavy\" find more on them here\r\nhttps://revengeofthepsychotronicman.bandcamp.com'),
('WsjGOVK2hpk', 'Think you\'ve had a Busy Year.....See this', 'To get a COLINFURZE MERCH click here\nhttps://www.colinfurzeshop.com\n\nHoverbikes, 360 swings, Star Wars and loads of fireworks means an extra 2million subscribers and a lot of fun.\nThanks to all that watch and share my videos and lets hope 2017 is as good.\n\nOrder The Colin Furze book aimed at kids 6+ which is full of little projects to turn them into little inventors and loads of pictures of my previous projects http://smarturl.it/C-Furze\n\nSubscribe so not to miss 2017 https://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=colinfurze\n\nAll videos on the colinfurze youtube channel https://www.youtube.com/colinfurze\n\nCheck my other pages for news and pictures\nTwitter https://twitter.com/colin_furze\nInstagram https://www.instagram.com/realcolinfurze/\nFacebook https://www.facebook.com/Colin-furze-521680751253584', '2016-12-30', 1, NULL);
