('XbPtonRSzII', 'How to build a 60MPH MOBILITY SCOOTER #3 controls n systems', 'Part 3 of furzes guide to making an owsome mobility scooter. This video covers the repostioning of the carb setting out the electrics and the all important gear shifting set up.\n\nCheck my other pages for news and pictures\nTwitter https://twitter.com/colin_furze\nInstagram https://www.instagram.com/realcolinfurze/\nFacebook https://www.facebook.com/Colin-furze-521680751253584\nhttp://www.colinfurze.com\n\nPart 1 is here http://youtu.be/u6arzfzwqyo\n\nPart 2 is here http://youtu.be/cveCmTr-NnY\nAll links for everything used and a full written guide are avalible at my website\n\nhttp://www.colinfurze.com/index.html\n\nalso follow me on twitter https://twitter.com/colin_furze\n\nand my Facebook page https://www.facebook.com/pages/Colin-furze/521680751253584\n\nENJOY AND SUBSCRIBE TELL YOUR MUM AND BEST FRIEND', '2014-03-13', 1, NULL),
('XcPhHvOVk8Y', 'The Colin Furze BOOK!!!!', 'Oh yes Furze is doing a book, but not just any book, no this is a book to get the mini furzes out there building there own amazing projects.\n\nPre Order your copy now\n\nFrom UK: http://po.st/ThisBookIsntSafe\nFrom USA: http://www.penguinrandomhouse.com/books/563276/\n\nViewers from other countries can order through these link.\nhttps://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/0141386959/ref=cm_sw_r_cp_ep_dp_eRP2ybWMW74D8\n\nTo get a COLINFURZE MERCH click here\nhttps://www.colinfurzeshop.com\n\nIt contains ten awesome inventions that you can make yourself with an affordable toolkit!\nPlease note: inventions may need parental supervision.\n\nSocial stuff here people\nTwitter https://twitter.com/colin_furze\nInstagram https://www.instagram.com/realcolinfurze/\nFacebook https://www.facebook.com/Colin-furze-521680751253584', '2017-04-06', 1, NULL),
('Y6wOcXQ1ALQ', 'Karaoke Shower', 'In this episode of \"Furze\'s Invention Show\" I\'ve created an entry from the ODDKA Odd Invention Challenge of which I was a judge. The Karaoke Shower is the perfect device for all you fools that sing in the shower and sound crazy but with the KS you can sound a little bit better if not a bit more socially acceptable. More info on the comp in link below but this is a great example of how your ideas could be made a reality just by posting in the comments so get thinking i\'ve had some great ideas from people already.\n\nhttps://www.oddinvention.com\n\nIf you have an idea for an invention you would like me to make then either put it in the comments or send me a message then it could be your invention on the table.\n\nTo see all other episodes click on link below for full playlist.\n\nhttp://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLGjbAdaOBLBm0srtohPiOw5uyhyC0frBL\n\nThe song i\'m singing is i\'m to fat by March To The Grave and link is\nhttps://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/im-too-fat/id505574414?i=505574419&uo=4\n\nAlso subscribe so you don\'t miss any new shows.\n\nTo get COLINFURZE MERCH click here\nhttps://www.colinfurzeshop.com', '2015-01-22', 1, 'The song i\'m singing is i\'m to fat by March To The Grave and link is\r\nhttps://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/im-too-fat/id505574414?i=505574419&uo=4'),
