('gEUBLIFMgnY', '5000 shot Firework Deathstar', 'To get COLINFURZE MERCH click here\nhttps://www.colinfurzeshop.com\n\n5000 shots 59 fuses and 80m to leg it so i\'m not the target lol, To celebrate the colinfurze youtube channel hitting 3 Million subscribers as ever things are done epic and things are done big so the Firework deathstar was born.\n\nCheck out the other milestone Firework madness here\n1M - https://youtu.be/yQf5cGPcP48\n2M - https://youtu.be/tY5Wzjk0-Xs\n3M - https://youtu.be/gEUBLIFMgnY\n4M - https://youtu.be/5-e2tAUo89o\n5M - https://youtu.be/2esw8U2NENo\n6M - 6M - https://youtu.be/fzMi6yf1Roc\n7M - https://youtu.be/Jtols_QhuWw\n\nThanks to EpicFireworks for the supply, check more on them here\nhttps://epicfireworks.com/blog/2016/06/deathstar-fireworks-by-colin-furze/\n\nSee the 3 videos here\n\nHoverbike https://youtu.be/soxxPyaAT1k\n\nThermite https://youtu.be/JEoqrjFX1yI\n\nGuitar https://youtu.be/xwWw9g0EgHA\n\nKarl the drone operator has done a behind the scenes Vlog and thats here https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qV46k8JX7IY\n\nMusic is by \"Brawlers\" and the song called \"Two Minutes\" see more from them here http://www.ilovealcopop.co.uk\n\nSubscribe to the channel so 4m comes sooner.\n\n#fireworks #furze #amazing', '2016-06-09', 1, 'Music is by \"Brawlers\" and the song called \"Two Minutes\" see more from them here http://www.ilovealcopop.co.uk'),
