('sdcGek-NoFQ', 'DIY X-MEN WOLVERINE fully automatic claws', 'The first ever fully automatic wolverine claws that deploy AND retact automaticlly.\nCheck my other pages for news and pictures\nTwitter https://twitter.com/colin_furze\nInstagram https://www.instagram.com/realcolinfurze/\nFacebook https://www.facebook.com/Colin-furze-521680751253584\nhttp://www.colinfurze.com\n\nThese beuatiful 12\" stainless steel claws fire out at the touch of a button and bring me as close as anyone has to feeling like they have adamantium claws. I think these are best on the net so hope you like em.\n\nCheck out the next set of videos in my DIY X-MEN series. Magneto Shoes! http://youtu.be/sdcGek-NoFQ\n\nTheres more DIY X-MEN to come next thursday so subscribe you won\'t want to miss it.\n\nYou can see how they were made here\n\nhttp://youtu.be/fVBCFGebqTg\n\nMusic is by march to the grave but from what i\'m seeing in the comments its not there itunes so i\'ll find out\n\nhttps://itunes.apple.com/us/artist/march-to-the-grave/id293740174?uo=4\n\nENJOY AND REMEMBER LIKE SAID THIS THE BEST CHANNEL AND I\'M NOT JUST SAYING THAT.', '2014-05-15', 1, 'Music is by march to the grave but from what i\'m seeing in the comments its not there itunes so i\'ll find out\r\n\r\nhttps://itunes.apple.com/us/artist/march-to-the-grave/id293740174?uo=4'),
